{"tid":1850003,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人接觸過TG之後皮膚一直有問題?","createTime":"2020-01-29T10:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T04:30:17.000Z","uid":271354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c3f8fd34970a5141449437f19a65e151623ccea4","tid":1850003,"uid":271354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:26:58.000Z","msg":"困擾左好耐<br />\n8月生過風癩<br />\n之後皮膚一直有問題<br />\n最開頭係手腳紅腫 生粒粒 腫既地方有一細粒膿瘡<br />\n部分位置之後會爛 傷口變大 試過行路都痛到仆街<br />\n其他就淨係膿瘡位置變左傷口<br />\n傷口會痕 流膿 大部分都埋唔到口 <br />\n好番既小部分就變左疤痕<br />\n而加成對腳都爛晒 最爛既位置起碼3cm x 3cm<br />\n<br />\n11月揾過杏林醫生睇 食過抗生素 敷過膏布<br />\n但都係埋唔到口<br />\n到而加情況都係咁 <br />\n晚晚都流腫甚至流血 要用紗布遮住<br />\n<br />\n可以點搞 唔想成世都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad6e3d85e5973b932e29e4e2cf50904e18f3ae85","tid":1850003,"uid":141957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:40:38.000Z","msg":"細菌感染？<br />\n要睇醫生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b735b2ef574d8c57a40b870fd176c47de3bff6","tid":1850003,"uid":221198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:45:43.000Z","msg":"有冇圖<br />\n有冇流組織液?"},{"pid":"156d0a7dd5e4cb48143671d9bf1c11364aba7276","tid":1850003,"uid":271354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad6e3d85e5973b932e29e4e2cf50904e18f3ae85","tid":1850003,"uid":141957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:40:38.000Z","msg":"細菌感染？<br />\n要睇醫生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:40:49.000Z","msg":"唔知... 之前食左成個月抗生素"},{"pid":"dcd6524461f25d4240059475ab964d67c4d38e5c","tid":1850003,"uid":271354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2b735b2ef574d8c57a40b870fd176c47de3bff6","tid":1850003,"uid":221198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:45:43.000Z","msg":"有冇圖<br />\n有冇流組織液?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:42:02.000Z","msg":"有11月既圖<